snippet.title: NES Longplay [875] Disney's Aladdin
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: JohnX895

Port of the game with the Game Boy from Virgin itself. Very average, even we can say, weakly, looks. Neither dynamics, nor graphics - pirate ports are on all headlines above this officially published game. -
